1. *Suprugu* sam upoznao pre pet godina. (I met *my spouse* five years ago.)
2. *Suprugu* je sinoć pozvao jedan stari prijatelj. (One old friend called *my spouse* last night.)
3. U restoranu je bilo više parova, ali smo primetili samo *suprugu* našeg kolege. (There were more couples in the restaurant, but we noticed only *the spouse* of our colleague.)
4. Naša kuma i njen *suprug* su izrazili želju da nas posete naredne nedelje. (Our godmother and her *husband* expressed a desire to visit us next week.)
5. *Supruga* je odlučila da se preseli u drugi grad, a on ju je podržao u toj odluci. ( *The spouse* decided to move to another city, and he supported her in that decision.)
6. Moj *supružnik* i ja smo zajedno proveli divan dan u prirodi. (My *spouse* and I spent a wonderful day together in nature.)
7. *Supruzi* je potrebna pomoć oko kućnih poslova, pa ću joj danas pomoći. (*The spouse* needs help with household chores, so I'll help her today.)
8. Naš *suprug* voli da sprema hranu, pa sam mu kupila novi set posuđa za rođendan. (Our *husband* likes to cook, so I bought him a new set of cookware for his birthday.)
9. *Supruzi* sam kupio lepu ogrlicu za godišnjicu braka. (I bought a nice necklace for *my spouse* on our wedding anniversary.)
10. Danas idemo u posetu *supruzi* moje sestre. (Today we are visiting *my sister's spouse*.)